<?xml version="1.0" encoding="UTF-8"?><song><title>shì shéi ràng wǒ men ān rú pán shí 迦南846</title>
<lyrics>[V1]
 shì shéi ràng wǒ men ān rú pán shí shì shéi ràng wǒ men dà yǒu pàn wàng?
 shì shéi ràng wǒ men zuò zài zūn zhǎng de chē zhōng? shì shéi ràng wǒ men zǒu lù gāng qiáng?
 shì yé sū, fù huó de jiù zhǔ tā shì zhì lǐ quán de de dà jūn wáng.
 wǒ men yī kào tā yǒng bù dòng yáo. lái a wǒ men yào xiàng tā gē chàng.
 lái a wǒ men yào xiàng tā gē chàng.</lyrics>
<hymn_number>846</hymn_number>
<author>lǚ xiǎo mǐn</author>
</song>